{"tid":1219392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致 所有6/12冇參與嘅人","createTime":"2019-06-13T19:54:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T20:11:58.000Z","uid":69037,"like":17,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d53107d637788f5299f35fbf1ae151bab3f23ddd","tid":1219392,"uid":69037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:54:28.000Z","msg":"請問你地去左邊度?<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">SHAME ON YOU</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n當日大部分係90後<br />\n亦見到有好多00後嘅中學生<br />\n有男有女<br />\n佢地幫你捱左好多警棍、胡椒噴霧、催淚水劑、催淚彈、胡椒彈、布袋彈同橡膠子彈<br />\n<br />\n想問下你地幾多歲<br />\n相信唔會細得過班中學生<br />\n乜呢個社會唔係應該由我地班成年人去保護佢地<br />\n去建設一個更好嘅社會比班佢地咩?<br />\n點解要由班中學生幫你地受傷 幫你地抗爭?<br />\n佢地冒嘅風險比你地更大<br />\n未來重有好長嘅路<br />\n但你地連請一日假都唔肯<br />\n<br />\n當日好多學生第一次食催淚彈<br />\n好多女仔都驚到喊<br />\n佢地非常勇敢<br />\n但你地連企都冇企係佢地後面<br />\n要求唔多 唔該你地做返自己嘅本份<br />\n<br />\n有人比人拉左要告佢暴動罪<br />\n當日係有好多人有參加呢個抗爭<br />\n我呼籲一百萬人去自首<br />\n林鄭唔洗起樓喇 起監獄啦"},{"pid":"fdff528e68b75c40662eb0bf8824f61bb909a45a","tid":1219392,"uid":69037,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:59:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=63&amp;v=WlwiuzqfjHo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D63%26v%3DWlwiuzqfjHo&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADfRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=6ccf1166\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=63&amp;v=WlwiuzqfjHo</a><br />\n請你地反省同對班後生仔女道歉!"},{"pid":"95849e0e602175a935bba19d95be20724fd72ea3","tid":1219392,"uid":69037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T20:07:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1Ch9c1P0XbM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1Ch9c1P0XbM&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADfRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=706393b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1Ch9c1P0XbM</a>"},{"pid":"9752d4c2d42fe25b480dda9a528f2382e3fddb2b","tid":1219392,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T20:10:05.000Z","msg":"不好意思頭先唔小心負皮<br />\n我係想正皮<br />\n<br />\n我發夢嗰日自己食咗催淚<br />\n我有同感<br />\n<br />\n不過我覺得如果有好細嘅小朋友嘅父母就唔好兩個出曬<br />\n因為依家香港做嘅嘢都係為咗將來<br />\n但如果小朋友失去父母好好照顧同樣影響佢嘅將來"},{"pid":"57df933e00203256f7a2760ac853a23bbc1ed471","tid":1219392,"uid":153978,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T20:11:58.000Z","msg":"咪搞分化啦"}]}